---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Samartya Apps for Schools — Assistive Technology for Special Education" 
  description="Bring FreeSpeech and Dyslexia Reader to your school or district. Free evaluation copies. Apple VPP with 50% off for 20+ licenses. FERPA/COPPA compliant.">

  <Hero 
    title="Assistive technology that fits your classroom — and your budget."
    subtitle="FreeSpeech and Dyslexia Reader are used by speech-language pathologists, special educators, and AT specialists in school districts across the United States and schools in India. We make it easy to evaluate, purchase, and deploy."
    align="left"
    variant="alt"
  >
    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <Button href="/for-schools/request-trial">Request a Free Evaluation</Button>
      <Button href="/for-schools/pricing" variant="outline">See Pricing</Button>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="visual">
       <div class="video-placeholder">
        <div class="box">Classroom image showing students and educators</div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-12">Why Schools Choose Samartya Apps</h2>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <Card title="Evidence-Based">
          <p>Both apps are rooted in published research, not just good intentions. FreeSpeech's visual grammar system was featured in a TED talk and recognized by MIT Technology Review. Dyslexia Reader's strategies come from 20+ years of clinical work by the Madras Dyslexia Association.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card title="Therapist- and Teacher-Friendly">
          <p>Designed in collaboration with SLPs and educators. Features like challenge creation, adjustable scaffolding, and cloud-based material sharing fit into real IEP sessions and classroom workflows.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card title="Affordable at Scale">
          <p>Both apps support Apple's Volume Purchase Program with a 50% discount for purchases of 20 or more licenses. One-time purchase and subscription options are both available.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card title="Cross-Platform & Privacy-Compliant">
          <p>Available on iOS and Android. Dyslexia Reader is also coming to the web. Samartya Apps is committed to student data privacy and operates in a FERPA/COPPA compliant manner.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-primary">
    <div class="container text-center max-w-m mx-auto">
      <h2 class="mb-12">How to Evaluate</h2>
      
      <div class="timeline text-left">
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Request a free trial.</h3>
            <p>Fill out the form below and we'll send you extended evaluation access (30 days) to one or both apps, with no commitment. We can also provide promo codes for your colleagues to try the apps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Use it with students.</h3>
            <p>Try FreeSpeech in a speech therapy session. Upload a student's actual reading material into Dyslexia Reader. See how it fits into your existing intervention plans.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Share with your team.</h3>
            <p>We'll provide a one-page administrator's guide that you can share with your director of special education. It includes feature summaries, evidence base, pricing, and compliance information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Purchase.</h3>
            <p>Order through Apple VPP, Google Play managed distribution, or contact us for a purchase order or invoice. We respond to all institutional inquiries within one business day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <Button href="/for-schools/request-trial">Request a Free Evaluation →</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .mb-12 { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-12); }
  .mt-12 { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); }
  .text-left { text-align: left; }
  
  .max-w-m { max-width: 800px; }
  .mx-auto { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  .video-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .box {
    border: 2px dashed rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    padding: var(--spacing-8);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .grid-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-8);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-6);
  }
  
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-bg-surface);
  }
  
  .timeline-step {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }
  
  .timeline-step:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .step-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: calc((var(--spacing-6) + 16px) * -1);
    top: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--color-bg-surface);
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  
  .step-content h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
    color: var(--color-text-main);
  }
</style>
